com.facebook.buck.core.rules.modern

Interface HasCustomInputsLogic

  • All Known Implementing Classes:
    VersionedTool

    public interface HasCustomInputsLogic
    Deriving inputs directly from the @AddToRuleKey annotated fields of some objects doesn't work correctly or is too slow. When deriving inputs from an object that implements HasCustomInputsLogic, the framework (BuildableSupport / ModernBuildRule) will call computeInputs() instead of deriving from @AddToRuleKey fields.
